# Module 11: Pricing and Support 

## Overview
This module explains how AWS pricing works, what drives cloud costs, and how AWS helps customers **manage spending**, **optimize usage**, and **get support**.  
You also learn about cost optimization techniques, AWS Marketplace, and the AWS Partner ecosystem.

---

## Learning Objectives

| Objective | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| AWS Pricing Models | Understand how AWS services are priced |
| Cost Drivers | Identify factors that impact AWS costs |
| Cost Management | Learn tools for tracking and controlling spend |
| Support Plans | Compare AWS Support plans |
| Marketplace & Partners | Understand AWS Marketplace and the AWS Partner Network |
| Cost Optimization | Learn techniques to reduce cloud spending |

---

## Key Concepts of AWS Pricing

| Concept | Description |
|------|-------------|
| **Pay-as-you-go** | Pay only for what you use |
| **Scale benefits** | Lower costs as usage increases |
| **Elasticity** | Scale up and down to avoid overprovisioning |
| **Free Tier** | Limited free usage for new customers |

---

## Driving Factors of AWS Costs

| Cost Driver | Description |
|-----------|-------------|
| **Compute** | Instance type, size, and runtime |
| **Storage** | Amount stored, storage class |
| **Data Transfer** | Data moving out of AWS |
| **Requests** | API calls and service usage |
| **Region** | Pricing varies by AWS region |

---

## Amazon S3 Pricing

| Item | Description |
|----|-------------|
| **Service** | Amazon S3 |
| **Pricing Factors** | Storage used, requests, data transfer |
| **Free Tier** | Limited storage and requests |
| **Use Cases** | Data lakes, backups, static websites |
| **Resource Link** | https://aws.amazon.com/s3/pricing/ |

---

## Amazon EC2 On-Demand Pricing

| Item | Description |
|----|-------------|
| **Service** | Amazon EC2 |
| **Pricing Model** | Pay per second/hour with no commitment |
| **Pricing Factors** | Instance type, region, OS |
| **Use Cases** | Flexible workloads |
| **Resource Link** | https://aws.amazon.com/ec2/pricing/on-demand/ |

---

## AWS Organizations

| Item | Description |
|----|-------------|
| **Service** | AWS Organizations |
| **Purpose** | Centralized account management |
| **Billing Benefit** | Consolidated billing |
| **Use Cases** | Multi-account environments |
| **Resource Link** | https://docs.aws.amazon.com/organizations/latest/userguide/orgs_introduction.html |

