## AWS Billing Console

| Item | Description |
|----|-------------|
| **Service** | AWS Billing Console |
| **Purpose** | View and manage AWS charges |
| **Benefits** | Invoice access, credits, discounts |
| **Use Cases** | Cost tracking and reporting |
| **Resource Link** | https://docs.aws.amazon.com/awsaccountbilling/latest/aboutv2/billing-what-is.html |

