## AWS Support Plans

| Plan | Key Features |
|----|-------------|
| **Basic** | Free documentation and forums |
| **Developer** | Business hours support |
| **Business** | 24/7 support, faster response |
| **Enterprise** | Dedicated technical account manager |

---

## Additional AWS Support Options

| Support Option | Description |
|---------------|-------------|
| **AWS re:Post** | Community-driven Q&A platform |
| **AWS Trust & Safety Center** | Abuse reporting and guidance |
| **AWS Professional Services** | Hands-on expert assistance |
| **AWS Documentation** | Official technical resources |

