## AWS Partner Network (APN)

| Topic | Description |
|------|-------------|
| **Role** | Help customers adopt AWS |
| **Benefits** | Specialized expertise |
| **Partners** | Consulting, technology partners |

---

## AWS Partner Benefits

| Benefit | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| **Funding** | Credits and discounts |
| **Training** | AWS certifications and courses |
| **Events** | Webinars and workshops |

---

## Cost Optimization Techniques

| Technique | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| **Right-sizing** | Match resource size to workload |
| **Reserved Instances** | Lower cost for long-term use |
| **Savings Plans** | Flexible cost savings |
| **Monitoring** | Track unused resources |
| **Automation** | Shut down idle services |

---

## Summary
In Module 11, you learned how AWS pricing works, how to manage costs, and how AWS supports customers through tools, documentation, partners, and support plans.  
These services help ensure efficient spending, operational awareness, and access to expert guidance throughout your AWS journey.

